snippet.title: Loot River - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Start exploring Loot River on May 3rd!

Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1494260

Set in a series of procedurally generated labyrinths, Loot River is a dungeon crawling action roguelike that combines tense, real-time combat and dark fantasy settings with spatial block-shifting. 

Coming to Game Pass, Xbox and PC!

https://lootriver.com/
